to pass through the tunnel.

25
00:02:45,794 --> 00:02:47,387
Thank you.

26
00:02:47,463 --> 00:02:49,057
Uh, next Tuesday, then, same time?

27
00:02:49,131 --> 00:02:53,071
No. Uh, I don't think
I'm going to continue with our lessons.

28
00:02:53,135 --> 00:02:54,364
Oh, no.

29
00:02:55,571 --> 00:02:56,561
You're giving up?

30
00:02:57,573 --> 00:02:58,700
No.

31
00:03:00,142 --> 00:03:01,735
Oh.

32
