Okay.

33
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,504
Well...

34
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:05,513
good-bye.

35
00:03:05,581 --> 00:03:06,810
Good-bye.

36
00:03:08,650 --> 00:03:10,084
Uh, Mr. Vale.

37
00:03:10,151 --> 00:03:11,084
May I ask?

38
00:03:11,152 --> 00:03:13,885
How many teachers
have you had before me?

39
00:03:15,491 --> 00:03:16,424
Four.

40
00:03:16,492 --> 00:03:17,721
Well, for what it's worth,

41
00:03:17,792 --> 00:03:21,094
learning an instrument
at your age is difficult,

42
