77
00:06:11,395 --> 00:06:13,422
So I can stay focused on my book.

78
00:06:16,433 --> 00:06:18,129
Charles, I would really rather not go.

79
00:06:18,201 --> 00:06:21,766
Well, I'm sorry, but there really
isn't another option at this point.

80
00:06:26,275 --> 00:06:28,370
Charles, the truth is...

81
00:06:28,444 --> 00:06:30,311
this is really Shelley's paper.

82
00:06:30,379 --> 00:06:33,442
I just agreed to co-author it
because she asked me to.

83
00:06:35,118 --> 00:06:37,452
I'm not really prepared to present it.

84
00:06:38,454 --> 00:06:39,752
Now, look, Walter,
you can take it up

85
00:06:39,822 --> 00:06:40,983
with the Dean if you want,

86
00:06:41,056 --> 00:06:45,464
but as your friend, I wouldn't advise it,
not with that argument.

87
00:08:57,089 --> 00:08:58,079
Hello?

88
00:09:58,415 --> 00:10:00,078
Aah! Aah! Aah! Get out!

89
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:02,518
- I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
- Get out!

90
00:10:02,585 --> 00:10:03,575
You stay away from me!

91
00:10:03,653 --> 00:10:05,486
You leave me alone!

92
00:10:05,555 --> 00:10:07,422
No. I... It's... It's okay. I... I'm...

93
