234
00:19:44,018 --> 00:19:45,145
Welcome home.

235
00:19:45,219 --> 00:19:46,209
Hi.

236
00:19:50,224 --> 00:19:51,453
How was the conference?

237
00:19:51,525 --> 00:19:53,050
It was fine.

238
00:19:54,228 --> 00:19:56,163
Sorry about the pants. I...

239
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:58,222
I've been practicing
like this since I was a kid.

240
00:20:06,239 --> 00:20:08,175
You... You don't have
to stop practicing.

241
00:20:08,241 --> 00:20:10,541
Really? it won't bother you?

242
00:20:10,611 --> 00:20:12,945
- No. It's fine.
- Great.

243
00:20:21,087 --> 00:20:23,250
Hey, uh, Zainab's going to make dinner,

244
00:20:23,523 --> 00:20:25,254
if you want to eat with us later.

245
00:20:26,926 --> 00:20:28,088
Okay. Thank you.

246
00:20:42,908 --> 00:20:45,208
I'm sorry.
That was my mother in Michigan.

247
00:20:45,277 --> 00:20:49,217
